Goal
====

Create the world's first BBAAS (bulletin board as a service) in Python.

This will have the following features:
- shnazzy HTML5 UI
- developer-friendly API (curl -XPUT 'http://localhost:5000/item?name=foo')

Roadmap
=======

1. Choose a web framework (flask)
2. Learn how to use the web framework
3. Make the app
4. Profit?

Getting started
===============
```
cd into the directory
virtualenv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```